                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12918455" author="cmahnke" created="Wed, 6 Oct 2010 10:13:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;A simple Workaround:&lt;br/&gt;
MAVEN_OPTS=-Djava.awt.headless=true mvn package&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12918457" author="plindner" created="Wed, 6 Oct 2010 10:18:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Does this fix it for you?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;diff --git a/java/common/pom.xml b/java/common/pom.xml&lt;br/&gt;
index bfc7de3..583a04a 100644&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;#8212; a/java/common/pom.xml&lt;br/&gt;
+++ b/java/common/pom.xml&lt;br/&gt;
@@ -68,6 +68,12 @@&lt;br/&gt;
           &amp;lt;excludes&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
             &amp;lt;exclude&amp;gt;org/apache/shindig/common/testing/*.java&amp;lt;/exclude&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
           &amp;lt;/excludes&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
+          &amp;lt;systemProperties&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
+            &amp;lt;property&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
+              &amp;lt;name&amp;gt;java.awt.headless&amp;lt;/name&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
+              &amp;lt;value&amp;gt;true&amp;lt;/value&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
+            &amp;lt;/property&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
+          &amp;lt;/systemProperties&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
         &amp;lt;/configuration&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
       &amp;lt;/plugin&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
     &amp;lt;/plugins&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12918604" author="cmahnke" created="Wed, 6 Oct 2010 17:37:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Works for me, thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13241723" author="plindner" created="Thu, 29 Mar 2012 20:58:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;part of 2.5.0-beta1 release.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
